snippet.title: Ant-Eater for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

In Ant-Eater you play as an ant who has to collect food and put it in its colony.

But beware of the anteater(s)! But luckily you can kill them with the rocks underground.


What I think:

A nice game, but the music is horrendous and annoying.
